| Split               | `split.md`              | `tests/editing/split-phonebook.spec.ts`              | 10        | 8       | 3       | **Active (partial skips)** — 1 BUG skip: AC-010 ([FFP-82754](https://jira.corp.adobe.com/browse/FFP-82754))                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
| Trim                | `trim.md`               | `tests/editing/trim-phonebook.spec.ts`               | 11        | 6       | 4       | **Active (partial skips)** — 1 BUG skip: AC-003 ([FFP-82753](https://jira.corp.adobe.com/browse/FFP-82753))                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
| Selection           | `selection.md`          | `tests/editing/selection-phonebook.spec.ts`          | 10        | 8       | 3       | **Active (partial skips)** — 2 BUG skips: Shift+marquee ([FFP-82755](https://jira.corp.adobe.com/browse/FFP-82755)), Escape ([FFP-82756](https://jira.corp.adobe.com/browse/FFP-82756))                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
| Move (within-track) | `move.md`               | `tests/editing/move-phonebook.spec.ts`               | 8         | partial | several | **Active (partial skips)** — phonebook spec exists. Other active specs: `tests/same-track-drag.spec.ts`, `tests/cross-track-move.spec.ts`, `tests/cross-track-move-multi-select.spec.ts`, `tests/cross-track-create-new-track.spec.ts`, `tests/cross-track-drag-visuals.spec.ts`, `tests/multi-select-horiz-move.spec.ts`. Cross-track AC-003/003b and move-to-new-track AC-004/004b are `test.fixme` in the phonebook spec; snap-during-move AC-002/AC-005 are `test.skip` (covered by non-phonebook `tests/editing/freeform-snap-move.spec.ts` with indicator-only assertions). Known gap: uniform multi-select delta and destination-track identity not asserted. |
