| Freeform behavior   | `freeform-behavior.md`  | `tests/editing/freeform-behavior-phonebook.spec.ts`  | 12        | 6       | 4       | **Active (partial skips)** — 2 BUG skips: AC-004, AC-008b                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
| Snapping            | `snapping.md`           | `tests/editing/snapping-phonebook.spec.ts`           | 6         | 4       | 3       | **Active (partial skips)** — 4 inner `test.skip`/`test.fixme`: move-snap-to-clip-edge (AC-002, AC-005), move-snap-to-playhead, indicator-disappears-mid-drag, indicator-spans-full-height                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
