**Subtotal: ~117 ACs with a phonebook spec file in place** (plus dimension variants and error states beyond the named ACs; Playback's 25 ACs
remain phonebook-unclaimed, Move's 8 are now covered by `move-phonebook.spec.ts` plus five non-phonebook specs).

### Not ready (not implemented in FFP — fixme stubs only)

| Feature                | Phonebook file               | ACs (map) | Status          |
| ---------------------- | ---------------------------- | --------- | --------------- |
| Copy/cut/paste         | `copy-cut-paste.md`          | 4         | Not implemented |
| Duplicate              | `duplicate.md`               | 8         | Not implemented |
